;W[qq]LB[ns:1][rs:2][qr:3][qq:4]C[Dia.2 The 2,1 point

The 2,1 point is sure popular.  If Black takes at 1 then White can play on the vital point and live.  Black 3 doesn't mean anything, White can just play 4, and he just doesn't have liberties to do anything to White.
